attributionInfo.brokerName: Oceans Luxury Realty Full Service LLC

data.description:
Welcome to your dream beachside retreat! This two-bedroom, two-bathroom home offers an irresistible combination of comfort and convenience, perfectly complemented by its fantastic location with easy access to the beach, inviting you to embrace the coastal lifestyle.As you step into the living room, you'll be greeted by the warm ambiance of a fireplace, creating a cozy atmosphere for relaxation and gatherings. The master bedroom is a true haven, featuring a luxurious en suite with his and her sinks and a rejuvenating jacuzzi tub--your private sanctuary for unwinding after a day by the ocean. The chef-inspired kitchen is a culinary masterpiece, boasting wood cabinets, granite countertops, a gas range, and stainless steel appliances, ensuring a delightful cooking experience. Step outside into your fenced yard and onto the wood deck, where outdoor entertaining becomes a delight. The 12x12 storage building provides ample space for all your beach essentials, ensuring a clutter-free and organized home. The property also features an inside laundry area and an oversized one-car garage, adding to the overall convenience. This home has undergone thoughtful upgrades, making it a truly modern and turnkey residence:
New backyard wood deck in 2019
Kitchen remodeled in 2019
New refrigerator and dishwasher in 2019
Upgraded PVC sewer and waterlines under the house in 2020
Three-mil plastic moisture barrier in crawlspace in 2020
Master bedroom and master bathroom remodel in 2020
New roof in 2021
New AC system in 2021
Installation of a new continuous hot water heater in 2022
Natural gas line extended to the backyard in 2022
Upgraded gas range and microwave in 2022
Brand new Samsung washer and dryer in 2023
Noteworthy features include a total interior repaint with new baseboards and restored original wood floors in 2017, as well as a concrete front patio added in 2019. This meticulously maintained and thoughtfully upgraded home is a rare find, offering you the opportunity to enjoy the coastal lifestyle in comfort and style. Don't miss the chance to make this beachside gem your own!
